data.description: Get ready for a ''surprise'' like no other! Come on down today and take a gander at this fantastic property, and I promise it won't disappoint. Nestled in Surprise, Arizona, this abode is as clean as a whistle. This corner unit's curb appeal shines like a diamond, making it a real showstopper in the neighborhood. Step inside & you'll love the cozy downstairs living spaces. The family room, dining room, and eat-in kitchen may be small in size, but they boast a fantastic flow that makes the most of every sq. ft. As you make your way upstairs, you'll discover two generously sized bedrooms, each with its own private in-suite bathroom. These spacious retreats provide ample room for relaxation and privacy, ensuring that you'll have all the space you need to unwind and rejuvenate after a long day
